videos.headline: Howell connects with Brown for 39-yard UNC TD
videos.description: Sam Howell throws a deep ball to the end zone and Dyami Brown makes the difficult catch to score a 39-yard touchdown that gives UNC a 7-0 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Howell connects with Brown for 39-yard UNC TD) 2029/12/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Newsome juggles and makes incredible  grab in the corner of the end zone
videos.description: Sam Howell airs it out to Dazz Newsome who makes a juggling catch and manages to get one foot down in the corner of the end zone to score a UNC touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Newsome juggles and makes incredible TD grab) 2019/12/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Howell makes the TD catch to extend UNC lead to 41-6
videos.description: UNC uses a bit of trickery as Rontavius Groves completes a short pass to Sam Howell for a 2-yard touchdown in the third quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Howell makes the TD catch to extend UNC lead to 41-6) 2019/12/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Temple's Davis navigates through UNC D for 45-yard TD
videos.description: Todd Centeio completes a pass to Re'Mahn Davis, who weaves his way up the field to score a 45-yard Temple touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Temple's Davis navigates through UNC D for 45-yard TD) 2019/12/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: UNC's Newsome makes TD grab over two defenders
videos.description: Sam Howell airs it out to a backpedaling Dazz Newsome who is able to snag the catch in heavy traffic and get one foot down in the corner of the end zone.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UNC’s Newsome makes TD grab over two defenders) 2019/12/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mack Brown gets a Gatorade bath
videos.description: UNC players empty the Gatorade cooler on Mack Brown's head in the waning moments of the fourth quarter to celebrate the team's win over Temple at the Military Bowl.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Mack Brown gets a Gatorade bath) 2019/12/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Newsome makes 2 spectacular TD grabs in UNC's Military Bowl win
videos.description: Dazz Newsome shows off his receiving skill, making two difficult catches in the corner of the end zone as UNC takes down Temple in the Military Bowl 55-13.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Newsome makes 2 spectacular TD grabs in UNC’s Military Bowl win) 2019/12/27 ESHEET SOTFULL
